From ebab5ab770f8d6c3abf2c4dfd480895461c8db91 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Mon, 13 Jul 2026 23:58:34 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] Capture shared browser pointer streams

A drag may wander, a wheel may roam,
but captured gestures still know home.
Miss the pane and terminals reply;
hit the browser and no bytes slip by.
